  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-2dce2fc7-7fff-6232-4ed5-bfd5cca10f23&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Prior to superstructure works, detailed specification, a drainage layout and a management &amp;amp; maintenance plan (where applicable) of at least one suitable sustainable drainage system (i.e. water butt with overflow, raingarden, bioretention planter box, living roof (substrate depth of 80-150mm excluding the vegetative mat), permeable paving etc.) for the new lightwell shall be submitted to, and approved by the LPA. The drainage hereby approved shall be constructed in full and shall be retained in perpetuity thereafter. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-3b4d37ff-7fff-f750-6393-c7f0055cfb10&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;REASON&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;To ensure suitable sustainable drainage systems are provided. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "<p>The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this permission.</p><p><br></p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\nREASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).</p><p>\r\n</p>",
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.\r\n</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.\r\n</p>"
